trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.Compiler"></xref> objects.
This class cannot be inherited.
The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.CompilerCollection> does not refer to any actual element in the underlying configuration file.
It is a construct that allows easy access to the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.Compiler> objects it contains.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilerCollection"></xref> class.
Gets all the keys of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilerCollection"></xref>.
You can use this array to access the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.Compiler> objects contained in the collection.
The `string` array containing the collection keys.
Gets the type of the configuration collection.
The <xref href="System.Configuration.ConfigurationElementCollectionType"></xref> object of the collection.
Gets the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.Compiler"></xref> collection element at the specified index.
An integer value specifying a <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.Compiler"></xref> within the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilerCollection"></xref>.
A <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.Compiler"></xref> object.
Gets the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.Compiler"></xref> collection element for the specified language.
The language for the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.Compiler"></xref> object within the collection.
A <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.Compiler"></xref> object.
Gets the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilerCollection"></xref> key name at the specified index.
An integer value specifying a <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.Compiler"></xref> within the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilerCollection"></xref>.
The key name at the specified index of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilerCollection"></xref>.
Gets the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.Compiler"></xref> at the specified index of the collection.
If the compiler object does not exist in the collection, an out-of-range exception is thrown.
An integer value specifying a <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.Compiler"></xref> within the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.CompilerCollection"></xref>.
A <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.Compiler"></xref> object.
Gets the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.Compiler"></xref> collection element for the specified language.
Provides a semicolon-separated list of language names supported by the language provider.
The language for the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.Compiler"></xref> object within the collection.
A <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.Compiler"></xref> object.
